{
  "texts": [
    "In Table 1 we provide relevant datasets description.",
    "Our annotation task consists of labelling a tweet for either (1) one or more of 10 symptoms of depression (See next section), (2) No Evidence of Depression (NoED),",
    "(3) Evidence of Depression (ED) or (4) Gibberish.",
    "We have 10 labels instead of the traditional nine depression symptoms labels because we separate the symptom \"Agitation / Retardation\" into two categories so that our model can separately learn and distinguish these labels, unlike previous research (Yadav et al., 2020).",
    "NoED indicates the absence of any depression symptoms expressed in a tweet."
  ]
}